They arrived in full dinner suits, glittery all-in-one numbers and the latest in jacket fashions - but this is not Paris Fashion Week.

It is day three of Crufts 2015 where the preened and pampered of the canine world gather to compete in the world's biggest dog breed competition.

From Afghans in headdresses, to a terrier in a pram, day three of the event at the NEC arena in Birmingham has seen some incredible sights.

