Crufts is ultimately a celebration of all dogs. It celebrates working dogs, such as those in the Gamekeeper classes or which line up for the Police Dog Team Operational and Humanitarian Action of the Year award. 

The dogs compete in various events to test their obedience and agility in order to be named Best In Show. 

